Text: Can you find the C.E. Murphy series, The Walker Papers?  I think I'm missing some short stories. Something I've begun to love and depend on with internet files.

Great collection.  I belong to two book clubs and its always a chore to find a book to recommend that has some substance behind it.   This is a great resource, once I filter out all of the chick type books.
You are incredible! Thank you so much!!
